的核心企业，也是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">电梯行业内硕果仅存的国有电梯企业</span></strong>。经过数十载的努力与发展，广日电梯在二十世纪末步入&ldquo;中国电梯十大品牌&rdquo;行列，并当选&ldquo;全国政府采购电梯值得信赖品牌&rdquo;及&ldquo;2014-2016年中国房地产开发企业首选供应商品牌&quot;。 广日电梯以乘客电梯、无机房电梯、自动扶梯、自动人行道、观光电梯、载货电梯等为主导产品，集产品研发、设计、制造、安装、售后服务于一身。2009年实现制造基地整体升级搬迁后，进驻华南地区最大的电梯整机及配件制造基地---占地30万平方米的番禺区广日工业园，坐拥华南地区最大的电梯零部件及关联产业制造园区，实现制造、物流服务的快速响应。"},{"pid":"cfd556328d8ed7e01081cdef87e3b916a712d52b","tid":661420,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c20460bbd0e6557603b8062d213da98924964c","tid":661420,"uid":26156,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b05b33f028f5548f68effe28c65eef3e3a9de6b","tid":661420,"uid":185683,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"好睇係廿幾年前既價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係呢幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1f650260e51cb8693e86b4eb4eaed864aee07f","tid":661420,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大陸出品竟然用到26年先壞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>算係咁<br />\n<br />\n仲要26年前既中國<br />\n<br />\n當時中國科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>好睇係廿幾年前既<span style=\"color: red;\">貨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係呢幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f2d65a838efc13b56